{"tid":467344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"剩係屌人去淘寶冇骨氣係冇用, 要俾選擇人先得架","createTime":"2017-11-13T12:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T13:18:11.000Z","uid":16970,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62f89ecec00ad788f8a2cc37d790b28ac9d0b684","tid":467344,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"啲人幫襯淘寶, 就係因為平, 快, 方便, 上網就可以搵到商家. 覺得依啲特點重要嘅人, 同佢地講幾多幫襯中國呀, 骨氣呀, 都係冇用架.<br />\n<br />\n真係想依啲人去幫襯香港本地商家, 就整個本地商家嘅目錄, 佢地賣啲咩, 有咩特點, 啲人又係一上個目錄就搵到自己想要嘅嘢, 咁先可能有少少機會可以說服依班淘寶用戶去轉軚幫襯本地商家咋.<br />\n<br />\n要說服人, 唔好剩係講自己想講嘅嘢, 剩係sell自己覺得重要嘅觀點, 有時都要企晌對面諗下, 先可以推動到人地做你想佢地做嘅嘢呀."},{"pid":"b414313d01a2864cd7896abdcc60df276aa1fccd","tid":467344,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:08:27.000Z","msg":"食魚巴仲係咁認真上時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a79121fe63f97a7bd68fd15c86e50ec9366e24","tid":467344,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食魚巴仲係咁認真上時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等開飯咪打下字囉."},{"pid":"4e88d0763bd11e02f1a2d5fb3d56b343072e050b","tid":467344,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：褒義"},{"pid":"0e24e6a867a4c672296e9bfce1f17d4c5cf80239","tid":467344,"uid":16970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：褒義</blockquote><br />\n又唔係正能量, 只不過齋屌係唔會改變到件事."},{"pid":"e09